"title": "5724: offspring",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5724",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Literally, physical descendants, and figuratively, the recipients of a spiritual inheritance.</p>\n<h2>Physical offspring</h2>\n<h3>Offspring as physical descendants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:7\">GEN 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:15-Gen13:16\">GEN 13:15–13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:19\">NUM 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:12\">RUT 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:9\">ISA 61:9</a></p>\n<h3>Offspring as a blessing to parents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:3-Ps127:5\">PSA 127:3–127:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:6-Gen21:7\">GEN 21:6–21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:14\">DEU 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:41-Luke1:45\">LUK 1:41–1:45</a></p>\n<h3>Offspring as a blessing to others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:14\">GEN 28:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:17-Gen22:18\">GEN 22:17–22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:12-2Sam7:13\">2SA 7:12–7:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:11-1Chr17:12\">1CH 17:11–17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:76-Luke1:79\">LUK 1:76–1:79</a></p>\n<h3>Absence of offspring seen as a sadness or curse</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:2-Gen15:3\">GEN 15:2–15:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:20\">LEV 20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:9\">PSA 109:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:30\">JER 22:30</a></p>\n<h3>Steps to be taken to provide offspring under the law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:5-Deut25:6\">DEU 25:5–25:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:10\">RUT 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:13\">RUT 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:24\">MAT 22:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:19\">MRK 12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:28\">LUK 20:28</a></p>\n<h3>Offspring as a result of God's special intervention</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:11\">HEB 11:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:1-Gen21:2\">GEN 21:1–21:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21\">GEN 25:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:2-Judg13:3\">JDG 13:2–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:11-Luke1:13\">LUK 1:11–1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:18-Rom4:21\">ROM 4:18–4:21</a></p>\n<h3>God's claim on the firstborn offspring</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:1-Exod13:2\">EXO 13:1–13:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:11-Exod13:16\">EXO 13:11–13:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:19-Exod34:20\">EXO 34:19–34:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:11-Num3:13\">NUM 3:11–3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:15-Num8:18\">NUM 8:15–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:22-Luke2:24\">LUK 2:22–2:24</a></p>\n<h3>Offspring can inherit parents' blessing or punishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:5-Exod20:6\">EXO 20:5–20:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:9-Deut5:10\">DEU 5:9–5:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:39\">LEV 26:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:28-Jer22:30\">JER 22:28–22:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:15-Hos9:17\">HOS 9:15–9:17</a></p>\n<h3>The fate of the offspring of the wicked</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:13-Job27:14\">JOB 27:13–27:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:28\">PSA 37:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:20-Isa14:22\">ISA 14:20–14:22</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual offspring</h2>\n<h3>Human beings, the offspring of God through creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26-Acts17:29\">ACT 17:26–17:29</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The offspring of Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:29\">GAL 3:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:31-John8:41\">JHN 8:31–8:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:13-Rom4:17\">ROM 4:13–4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:6-Rom9:8\">ROM 9:6–9:8</a></p>\n<h3>Believers, spiritual offspring through new birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3-John3:8\">JHN 3:3–3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:9\">1JN 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:17\">REV 12:17</a></p>",
